NINO - Sigorta No.
    Ring the National Insurance Number application line at 0800 141 2075, which is open from Monday to Friday between 8am and 6pm. 
    https://blog.remitly.com/immigration/how-to-get-an-ni-number-in-the-uk-a-guide-for-non-residents/
    16 weeks ....
    
    You can start work in the UK without a permanent NI number, 
    as long as you can prove to an employer that you are eligible to work in the UK. 
    All employers will ask new employees for their passport or Identity Card (Europe only) 
    (or you can supply a full birth certificate if you are from the UK)
    
